""problem sloving""
Ye error JavaScript mein common hota hai, especially jab aap ES module syntax use kar rahe hote hain. 
Ye error aapko batata hai ke aapne require ko ES module scope mein use kiya hai, jabki require CommonJS 
module syntax ka part hota hai.

Is error ka matlab hai ke aapko import keyword ka istemal karna chahiye agar aap ES module syntax use kar 
rahe hain. Aur agar aap CommonJS syntax use karna chahte hain toh aapko file ko .cjs extension se rename 
karna hoga ya fir package.json mein "type": "commonjs" specify karna hoga.

Yeh error aksar Node.js mein modules ke sath aata hai jab aap ES module syntax (import) use karte hain, 
lekin Node.js ab CommonJS syntax (require) ko bhi support karta hai. Is error ko fix karne ke liye, aapko
require ki jagah import ka istemal karna hoga ya fir file ko CommonJS format mein convert karna hoga.







